---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import paceSatellite from '../assets/pace-satellite.jpg';
---

<Layout title="About the PACE Satellite">
  <h1>About the PACE Satellite</h1>
  
  <section class="pace-info">
    <Image src={paceSatellite} alt="PACE Satellite" width={600} height={400} />
    <div class="info-text">
      <h2>PACE Mission</h2>
      <p>PACE (Plankton, Aerosol, Cloud, ocean Ecosystem) is a NASA satellite mission aimed at studying the interactions between the atmosphere and the ocean. The satellite launch is scheduled for 2024.</p>
      <h3>Primary Mission Goals:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Studying phytoplankton and its role in the global carbon cycle</li>
        <li>Investigating aerosols and their impact on climate</li>
        <li>Observing clouds and their interactions with aerosols</li>
        <li>Monitoring the health of oceans and water quality</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="data-collection">
    <h2>How PACE Collects Data</h2>
    <p>The PACE satellite is equipped with advanced instruments for data collection:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Ocean Color Instrument (OCI):</strong> A hyperspectral radiometer for measuring ocean color</li>
      <li><strong>Multi-angle Polarimeters:</strong> Two polarimeters for studying aerosols and clouds</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="video-container">
      <iframe 
        width="560" 
        height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q-eBqDJ0Mbs?si=vRJX9epsHFV5-wRw" 
        title="PACE Satellite Operation Animation" 
        style="border: none;"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="impact">
    <h2>Significance for Climate Change Studies</h2>
    <p>PACE data will help scientists better understand:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The role of oceans in the global carbon cycle</li>
      <li>The impact of aerosols on cloud formation and climate</li>
      <li>Changes in marine ecosystems and their consequences for the climate</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pace-info {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .info-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .data-collection, .impact {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pace-info {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .pace-info img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
